rows.label: tlk502201_msg0001
rows.name: Meh-meh?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0002
rows.name: What should we ask?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0003
rows.name: Ask about Salvager Ranks

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0004
rows.name: Ask if Mochimochi needs any help

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0005
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh?!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0006
rows.name:
Friends knowing about skill of
Mochimochi? Very sneaky indeed!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0007
rows.name:
Since day Mochimochi was born, Mochimochi
see salvagers come and go. Developed
great skill of judging salvager ability!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0008
rows.name:
Also, fair and honest is motto of
Mochimochi. So Mochimochi offer
service of ranking salvagers.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0009
rows.name:
Yes, yes... So friends want Mochimochi
to judge salvager ability.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0010
rows.name: All right, Mochimochi rank friends.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0011
rows.name:
But Mochimochi require small cash fee
for ranking service!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0012
rows.name:
Meh-meh?! Friends look at Mochimochi
with scornful eye?!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0013
rows.name:
Oh, but Mochimochi do good service!
When friends gain rank, give special
reward for free as present!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0014
rows.name:
So friends pay fee for
ranking now, yes?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0015
rows.name: Pay 100G?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0016
rows.name: Thanks greatly friends!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0017
rows.name:
Now let Mochimochi see...
Up-and-Coming Young Salvager Rex...
Salvager Rank should be...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0018
rows.name: Congratulations! Rex at Rank E!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0019
rows.name:
But by Mochimochi standards, that
still only baby of salvaging.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes, baby of baby salvager.
About same level as Hiyokkoo.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0021
rows.name:
Still, Mochimochi keep promise.
Give present for achieving of rank!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0022
rows.name:
Come see Mochimochi again after
doing much more salvage!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0023
rows.name:
Who know, maybe Mochimochi give friend
shiny new rank! For small fee!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0024
rows.name: What this?! Rex not even have rank?!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0025
rows.name:
Rex well-known young salvager
around Avaritia, but actually not
do salvaging lately at all?!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0026
rows.name:
Oh dear oh dear...
Mochimochi ashamed of Rex for even ask
ranking with such neglect of skills.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0027
rows.name: Come back when try harder.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0028
rows.name:
Meh-meh?!
Mochimochi not expect you to say that!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0029
rows.name:
Mochimochi not give rankings for favors!
Only give rankings for fee!
Friends understanding this?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0051
rows.name:
Mochimochi not have any problems.
Have plenty money, family all healthy,
nothing to ask at all!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0052
rows.name:
Well, perhaps one thing...
Sonnypon of Mochimochi a bit too friendly
with sonnypon of Meroro.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0053
rows.name:
Mochimochi worried sonnypon catch
lazybones disease!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0101
rows.name: Friends want ranking of salvager?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0102
rows.name:
Mochimochi can not wait to see how
much Rex improve salvaging skills!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0103
rows.name: Please hand over fee then.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0104
rows.name:
Finally, Mochimochi give present for
rank increase, just as promise!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0201
rows.name: Friends want ranking of salvager?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0202
rows.name:
Mochimochi can not wait to see how
much Rex improve salvaging skills!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0203
rows.name: Please hand over fee then.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0204
rows.name:
Now let Mochimochi see...
Baby-Level Salvager Rex...
Salvager Rank should be...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0205
rows.name:
Congratulations!
Increase to Rank D!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0206
rows.name: Rex polishing salvager skills quite well.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0207
rows.name:
By the way, Bahn-sama also Rank D.
Actually only quite ordinary as salvager.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0208
rows.name:
Come see Mochimochi again after
doing much more salvage!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0209
rows.name:
Who know, maybe Mochimochi give friend
shiny new rank! For small fee!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0210
rows.name: Finally, this is reward for rank increase!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0211
rows.name:
Hmmmm... Sad to say, but Rex
not ready to increase rank yet.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0212
rows.name:
Ranking change based on type of
treasure troves friends find by salvage.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0213
rows.name:
Do much more salvage,
then come back to Mochimochi!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0214
rows.name:
Meh-meh?! Friends notice sneaky
little price hike Mochimochi implement?!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0215
rows.name:
Hmph. No use complain.
Mochimochi still only give ranking for fee!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0301
rows.name:
Now let Mochimochi see...
Bahn-Level Salvager Rex...
Salvager Rank should be...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0302
rows.name:
Congratulations!
Increase to Rank C!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0303
rows.name:
Actually, Dad of Mochimochi also
Rank C. Equal skill to Dad at
age of friends is quite impressive.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0304
rows.name:
Incidentally, Rank C very good ranking
among salvagers of Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0305
rows.name:
Can earn enough moneys salvaging
to feast on mushrooms every day!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0401
rows.name:
Now let Mochimochi see...
Mushroom-Feast Salvager Rex...
Salvager Rank should be...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0402
rows.name:
Congratulations!
Increase to Rank B!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0403
rows.name:
Mochimochi only ever see salvager of
Rank B twice before in whole life.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0404
rows.name:
Dad of Bahn-sama...and
great-grannypon of Mochimochi!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0405
rows.name:
Great-Grannypon was true master of
salvage. Always bring back white shiny
treasure trove on every attempt.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0406
rows.name:
Great-Grannypon not around any more
though, so sometimes get called
Legendary Salvager.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0501
rows.name:
Now let Mochimochi see...
Legendary Salvager Rex...
Salvager Rank should be...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0502
rows.name:
Congratulations!
Increase to Rank A!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0503
rows.name:
Mochimochi never see salvager with skill
such as Rex before in whole life.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0504
rows.name:
Mochimochi see halo of saintly
salvagehood shine around Rex.
Too shiny to look.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0505
rows.name:
Maybe Mochimochi should worship Rex
actually...

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0506
rows.name: Praise be to Rex! Praise be to Rex!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0507
rows.name:
Anyway, Rank A very great to
achieve, but also sadly dead end.
No more ranks left to earn!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0508
rows.name: Please take final rank increase reward!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0509
rows.name:
Mochimochi very grateful to Rex for
letting Mochimochi rate salvager rank.
Was actually quite great honor.

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0510
rows.name: Thank you much, friends!

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0511
rows.name: Pay 200G?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0512
rows.name: Pay 500G?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0513
rows.name: Pay 1000G?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0514
rows.name: Pay 2000G?

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0515
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0516
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: tlk502201_msg0601
rows.name:
Mochimochi not inspired to talk to
non-salvager. Hardly worth moving
Mochimochi's mouth!
